The paper deals with action recognition in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning and feature analysis, which are also common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimodal learning (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of regularization and group selection, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
